ung@had.gov.hk<br />\n元朗 / 24753854 / enochyuen@had.gov.hk<br />\n北區 / 26751728 / wwchong@had.gov.hk<br />\n大埔 / 35802694 / eunice_hm_chan@had.gov.hk<br />\n西貢 / 37405375 / david_yw_chiu@had.gov.hk<br />\n沙田 / 21585430 / amy_chan@had.gov.hk<br />\n葵青 / 24267173 / kennethcheng@had.gov.hk<br />\n離島 / 28524337 / anthony_pw_li@had.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n公眾查閱候選人遞交的選舉廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eaplatform.gov.hk/eaplatform/jsp/terms_chi.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eaplatform.gov.hk%2Feaplatform%2Fjsp%2Fterms_chi.jsp&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=fb716653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eaplatform.gov.hk/eaplatform/jsp/terms_chi.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發揮香港人精神<br />\n咩都投訴一餐🙋🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\nEmail Sample:<br />\n投完票唔好咁快返屋企住，仲有嘢可以做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1750241\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1750241</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90babaf280ee0d0e243cbb1018b90a9aebec21da","tid":1750054,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db22d57e63feba13e17a1accb6caaf58d5119da4","tid":1750054,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"209a965d9bb08d4bd15f294250d05d6f5a5437eb","tid":1750054,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8b9e0d3329459dad702856dec1e8a76aed190a4","tid":1750054,"uid":1734,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"把口咁撚臭？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"笠狗得把口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢成日咀炮肉酸 但唔敢同佢隻秋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"肉酸出名廢j都唔敢同佢隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1a83d4416d6fe69b6a354345089a59ee731fbf","tid":1750054,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"301f376a5c1d4b5812669bfba7bc2ee895efed0b","tid":1750054,"uid":310434,"like":0,"dislike":